title: Lending in focus as Australian inquiry begins
text:
Lending in focus as Australian inquiry begins 1:23pm GMT - 01:39 
A government-backed inquiry into Australia's finance sector says it will start its year-long investigation by scrutinising the selling tactics of banks' most lucrative products - mortgages. Laura Frykberg reports.
